\c 6
\s Umtshokotsho wesivumelwano ubuyiselwa koIsrayeli
\p
\v 1 Lomtshokotsho weN\nd kosi\nd* wawuselizweni lamaFilisti inyanga eziyisikhombisa.
\v 2 AmaFilisti asebiza abapristi labavumisi\x + Dute. 18.10. Gen. 41.8. Eks. 7.11. Dan. 2.2. 5.7.\x*, esithi: Sizawenzelani umtshokotsho weN\nd kosi\nd*? Saziseni ukuthi singawuthumeza lani endaweni yawo.
\v 3 Basebesithi: Uba lingawuthumeza umtshokotsho kaNkulunkulu wakoIsrayeli, lingawuthumezi uze\x + Eks. 23.15.\x*, kodwa libuyisele lokubuyisela kuye umnikelo wecala\x + Levi 5.15,16.\x*. Khona-ke lizasiliswa, njalo kuzakwaziwa kini ukuthi kungani isandla sakhe singasuki kini\x + 6.9.\x*.
\v 4 Basebesithi: Uzakuba yini umnikelo wecala esizawubuyisela kuye? Basebesithi: Amathumba ophayo egolide amahlanu lamagundwane amahlanu egolide\x + Levi 11.29.\x*, njengokwenani leziphathamandla zamaFilisti\x + 6.17,18. Josh. 13.3.\x*; ngoba bekulenhlupheko eyodwa kini lonke lakuziphathamandla zenu.
\v 5 Ngakho lizakwenza imifanekiso yamathumba enu ophayo lemifanekiso yamagundwane enu alonayo ilizwe\x + 5.6.\x*, limnike udumo uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli\x + Josh. 7.19.\x*; mhlawumbe angenza lula isandla sakhe sisuke phezu kwenu\x + 5.6,9,11.\x* sisuke laphezu kwabonkulunkulu benu sisuke laphezu kwelizwe lenu\x + 5.3,4,7.\x*.
\v 6 Lenzelani-ke inhliziyo zenu zibe lukhuni njengamaGibhithe loFaro benza inhliziyo zabo zaba lukhuni\x + Eks. 8.15,32. 9.7,34. 10.1. Eks. 7.13.\x*? Emva kokuthi esenze kabuhlungu kubo kabavumelanga yini ukuthi bahambe, basebehamba\x + Eks. 12.31.\x*?
\v 7 Ngakho-ke thathani lilungise inqola entsha lamankomokazi amabili amunyisayo\x + 2 Sam. 6.3. Nani 7.3,6.\x* okungezanga jogwe phezu kwawo, liwabophele amankomokazi enqoleni, liwabuyisele ekhaya amankonyana awo asuke emva kwawo\x + Nani 19.2.\x*.
\v 8 Lithathe umtshokotsho weN\nd kosi\nd*, liwubeke enqoleni, lempahla zegolide elizibuyisela kuye zibe ngumnikelo wecala, lizifake ebhokisini eceleni kwawo; liyithumeze ihambe\x + 6.4,5.\x*.
\v 9 Libone aluba isenyuka ngendlela yomngcele wawo eya eBeti-Shemeshi\x + Josh. 15.10.\x*, yiyo esenzele lobububi obukhulu; kodwa uba kungenjalo, sizakwazi ukuthi kakusiso isandla sayo esisitshayileyo, sehlelwe yingozi nje\x + 6.3.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Abantu basebesenza njalo, bathatha amankomokazi amabili amunyisayo, bawabophela enqoleni, bawavalela amankonyana awo ekhaya.
\v 11 Bawubeka umtshokotsho weN\nd kosi\nd* enqoleni lebhokisi elilamagundwane egolide lezithombe zamathumba abo ophayo.
\v 12 Amankomokazi aseqonda endleleni, ngendlela eya eBeti-Shemeshi\x + Josh. 15.10.\x*, ahamba ngomgwaqo omkhulu\x + Nani 20.19.\x* ehamba ebhonsa, engaphambukeli ngakwesokunene loba ngakwesokhohlo, leziphathamandla zamaFilisti zawalandela kwaze kwaba semngceleni weBeti-Shemeshi.
\v 13 AbeBeti-Shemeshi babevuna isivuno sengqoloyi esigodini; lapho bephakamisa amehlo abo, bawubona umtshokotsho, bathokoza uku\add wu\add*bona.
\v 14 Inqola yasingena ensimini kaJoshuwa weBeti-Shemeshi, yema khona, lapho okwakulelitshe elikhulu khona; basebebanda izigodo zenqola, basebenikela amankomokazi aba ngumnikelo wokutshiswa eN\nd kosi\nd*ni.
\v 15 AmaLevi asewethula umtshokotsho weN\nd kosi\nd* lebhokisi elalilawo\x + Josh. 21.16.\x*, okwakukulo impahla zegolide, akubeka phezu kwelitshe elikhulu. Labantu beBeti-Shemeshi banikela iminikelo yokutshiswa, bayihlabela iN\nd kosi\nd* imihlatshelo ngalolosuku.
\v 16 Iziphathamandla ezinhlanu zamaFilisti sezikubonile\x + 6.4.\x*, zabuyela eEkhironi ngalolosuku\x + Josh. 15.11.\x*.
\p
\v 17 Lala ngamathumba ophayo egolide amaFilisti awabuyisela abe ngumnikelo wecala eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, eleAshidodi elilodwa\x + 5.1.\x*, eleGaza elilodwa\x + Josh. 15.47.\x*, eleAshikeloni elilodwa\x + Hlu. 1.18.\x*, eleGathi elilodwa\x + 17.4.\x*, eleEkhironi elilodwa\x + Josh. 15.11.\x*.
\v 18 Lamagundwane egolide njengokwenani lemizi yonke yamaFilisti yeziphathamandla ezinhlanu, kusukela emizini ebiyelweyo kuze kube semizaneni yemaphandleni\x + Dute. 3.5.\x* kuze kube se\add litshe\add*ni elikhulu likaAbeli, lapho ababeka khona umtshokotsho weN\nd kosi\nd*, \add eli\add*sensimini kaJoshuwa umBeti-Shemeshi kuze kube lamuhla\x + 6.19. Gen. 50.11. Hlu. 11.33.\x*.
\p
\v 19 Yasitshaya amadoda eBeti-Shemeshi ngoba ayekhangele phakathi komtshokotsho weN\nd kosi\nd*; yebo, yatshaya phakathi kwabantu amadoda azinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amahlanu lamatshumi ayisikhombisa\x + Eks. 19.21. Nani 4.5,15,20. 2 Sam. 6.7.\x*. Abantu basebelila ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* yayitshaye ngokutshaya okukhulu phakathi kwabantu\x + 6.19. Gen. 50.11. Hlu. 11.33.\x*.
\v 20 Ngakho abantu beBeti-Shemeshi bathi: Ngubani olakho ukuma\x + 2 Sam. 6.9.\x* phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*, lo uNkulunkulu ongcwele\x + Josh. 24.19.\x*? Uzakwenyukela kubani esuka kithi?
\p
\v 21 Basebethuma izithunywa kubahlali beKiriyathi-Jeyarimi besithi: AmaFilisti asewubuyisile umtshokotsho weN\nd kosi\nd*; yehlani liwenyusele kini\x + Josh. 9.17.\x*.